         <creation notBefore="1500">Author and date of writing not known. 

            A witness to the events narrated or a later elaboration (15th cent.?) upon unknown earlier source; cp.  <bibl><ptr target="bm:Chernetsov2007Hist"/> <citedRange unit="page">41</citedRange></bibl>.
            About various hypothesis on the dating, see <bibl><ptr target="bm:Marrassini1993AmdaSeyon"/><citedRange unit="page">39-43</citedRange></bibl>.
            
            A second redaction (<title xml:id="t2Haylu">Redaction Ḫaylu</title>) was promoted by daǧǧāzmāč <persName ref="PRS5222haylaMi">Ḫāylu</persName> around the year <date>1785</date> 
            (after rās <persName ref="PRS7091Mikael">Mikāʾēl</persName> set the historical archives of <placeName ref="LOC3577Gondar">Gondar</placeName> on fire)
         </creation>
