        <abstract>
           <p>
              Account of campaigns of  <persName ref="PRS1854Amdase">ʿAmda Ṣǝyon I</persName> against the Muslims of South-East Ethiopia. 
              </p>
           <p>
           According to <bibl><ptr target="bm:Marrassini1993AmdaSeyon"/><citedRange unit="page">43-46</citedRange></bibl>, 
              originally it was not a real historical work, but a homily to read in the church, with a propagandist purpose.
           </p>
        </abstract>
